e post(s) to trash?'=>'把文件移到垃圾箱吗？','If it’s necessary the process will dynamically slow down - depending on your server’s resource consumption. For example, if you’re using another plugin which is running a background process and it takes a lot of resources (+50%), our plugin will wait/slow down until the other process is complete.'=>'根据您的服务器资源消耗情况，删除进程会动态降低速度。例如，如果您在使用另一个插件，后台运行，消耗资源很多（+50%），那么，本插件将推迟/减速执行，直至另一个进程结束。','Enable this if you want to have your posts/pages getting deleted in batches (instead of all at once).<br />This reduces the risk of timeouts if you have a lot to delete.<br />'=>'如果希望按批删除文章/网页（而不是一次全部删除），请选择此项。<br />可以降低大量删除时超时风险。<br />','per minute'=>'每分钟','Delete'=>'删除','Deletion throttling'=>'删除速度控制','Enable this if you want to redirect the urls from your deleted posts/pages to the main one you decided to keep.'=>'如果希望把要删除的文章/网页重定向到保留的页面，请启用该选项。','Enabled'=>'已启用','Disabled'=>'已禁用','Automatic redirection'=>'自动重定向','Check if you need these features (optional):'=>'如需要以下功能，请选择（可选）：','Select all the posts & pages which should be deleted (by ticking the checkboxes in the table above).'=>'选择要删除的文章与网页（选择上面列表中的复选框）。','Make sure you created a backup with, e.g. with <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/backup-backup/" target="_blank">this plugin</a>.'=>'创建备份。可用<a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/backup-backup/" target="_blank">这个插件</a>。','Steps to deletion:'=>'删除步骤：','You selected <b class="cdp-t-d-ct cdp-f-w-light">0</b> pages/posts to be deleted'=>'已选择删除<b class="cdp-t-d-ct cdp-f-w-light">0</b>个网页/篇文章','<u class="cdp-d-select-all cdp-f-w-light">Select all</u> (also from other pages)'=>'<u class="cdp-d-select-all cdp-f-w-light">全选</u>（含列表其它页面）','# of words'=>'词数','Date created'=>'创建日期','Type'=>'类型','Slug/URL'=>'别名/URL','per page'=>'条记录','Show'=>'每页显示','Scan has found [<span id="cdp-d-table-pagi-ilosc-wynikow" class="cdp-f-w-bold"></span>] duplicates'=>'扫描出[<span id="cdp-d-table-pagi-ilosc-wynikow" class="cdp-f-w-bold"></span>] 个重复文件','Scan for duplicates now!<br /><small class="cdp-sm-d cdp-f-s-17 cdp-f-w-medium">(at this point nothing gets deleted)</small>'=>'马上扫描重复文件！<br /><small class="cdp-sm-d cdp-f-s-17 cdp-f-w-medium">（不会删除）</small>','<b>Filter results (optional)</b>: Only list them, if they<span id="cdpp-switch-mf"> […]</span>'=>'<b>过滤结果（可选）</b>: 只列出满足以下条件的文件：<span id="cdpp-switch-mf"> […]</span>','Delete ALL duplicates, don’t keep any (Be careful!)'=>'删除全部文件，不保留任何文件（要小心操作！）','Keep the newest duplicate (typically the last copy you made)'=>'保留最新的重复文件（通常是最近副本）','Keep the oldest duplicate (typically the original)'=>'保留最早的重复文件（通常是原文件）','Which version do you want to keep?'=>'要保留哪个版本？','Huh?'=>'什么意思？','Also count pages/posts of different types as duplicates'=>'包含不同内容类型（网页/文章）的重复文件','Only count pages/posts of the same type as duplicates'=>'只含同一内容类型（网页/文章）的重复文件','...need others? <a href="mailto:hi@copy-delete-posts.com" target="_blank">Suggest them!</a>'=>'……需要别的选项？<a href="mailto:hi@copy-delete-posts.com" target="_blank">欢迎推荐！</a>','Word count'=>'词数','Excerpt (<span class="cdp-no-empty-text"><b>including</b> empty</span>)'=>'摘要（<span class="cdp-no-empty-text"><b>含</b>空值</span>）','When does “yes” make sense here?'=>'什么时候选择“是”？','The copies you created may have been given different titles automatically (according to the rules in <a href="#" class="cdp-go-to-names-chapter">this section</a>) and therefore would not count as duplicates as they have different titles.<br /><br />To remedy this, you can select “Yes” here so that those posts/pages also get considered as duplicates.'=>'（根据<a href="#" class="cdp-go-to-names-chapter">这一部分</a>的规则），创建的副本自动带不同的文件名，文件名不同，所以不算重复。<br /><br />为解决这个问题，可以选择“是”，也把这些副本算作重复文件。','Yes'=>'是','No'=>'否','Do you want to consider different titles still to be identical if a) the copied posts/pages<br />were created by this plugin and b) they were not modified thereafter?'=>'如果副本 a) 由本插件生成，且 <br />b) 之后未修改，虽然标题不同，是否认为是重复？','Slugs are never 100% identical (i.e. Wordpress adds a counter automatically to ensure they are unique). The rule to only have them at least 85% identical does the job fine (you can see after the scan which posts are considered identical).'=>'别名永远不会重复（Wordpress会自动添加计数，来确保别名唯一性）。至少有85%相同，基本可以满足需要（扫描后可以检查一下，看是否重复）。','Similar slug'=>'相似的别名','(show more options)'=>'（更多选项）','Count them as duplicates if they are identical with respect to <u class="cdp-f-w-bold">all</u> of the below...'=>'如果满足以下<u class="cdp-f-w-bold">所有</u>条件，则认为是重复的。','Custom posts'=>'自定义文章','Scan for duplicates in...'=>'重复文件扫描范围……','Go premium now'=>'马上升级','And: you can also use this feature for any other redirections you may need
