.com/questions/25202/how-to-change-order-of-menu-items" target="_blank"><span class="cdp-green">menu order</span></a> from the original.'=>'……含<a href="https://wordpress.stackexchange.com/questions/25202/how-to-change-order-of-menu-items" target="_blank"><span class="cdp-green">菜单顺序</span></a>。','Menu order'=>'菜单顺序','…get no comments from the original.'=>'……不含评论。','…get all comments from the original.'=>'……含所有评论。','Comments'=>'评论','…not get their child pages copied along (if the page is a parent).'=>'……（如果网页为上级页面，）不含子页面。','…get their <a href="https://phppot.com/wordpress/how-to-create-a-child-page-in-wordpress/" target="_blank"><span class="cdp-green">child pages</span></a> copied as well, with all current settings applied to child-duplicates (if the page is a parent).'=>'……（如果网页为上级页面，）含<a href="https://phppot.com/wordpress/how-to-create-a-child-page-in-wordpress/" target="_blank"><span class="cdp-green">子页面</span></a>，且对子页面都应用当前设置。','Children'=>'子页面','…get existing attachments from the original.'=>'……含附件。','…create new <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/using-image-and-file-attachments/#attachment-to-a-post" target="_blank"><span class="cdp-green">attachments</span></a> (duplicates in Media Library) as well. <i>Recommended only for Multisites.</i>'=>'……生成新<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/using-image-and-file-attachments/#attachment-to-a-post" target="_blank"><span class="cdp-green">附件</span></a>副本（媒体库）。 <i>仅推荐对多网站采用。</i>','Attachments'=>'附件','…get no password.'=>'……不含密码。','…get the same <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/using-password-protection/" target="_blank"><span class="cdp-green">password</span></a> as original.'=>'……含原<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/using-password-protection/" target="_blank"><span class="cdp-green">密码</span></a>。','Password'=>'密码','…get the user that is duplicating as an author.'=>'……设定作者为执行复制操作的用户。','…get the same author as original.'=>'……含原作者。','Author'=>'作者','…get the standard post format.'=>'……含标准贴子格式。','…get the same <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/post-formats/" target="_blank"><span class="cdp-green">post format</span></a> as original.'=>'……含原<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/post-formats/" target="_blank"><span class="cdp-green">文章格式</span></a>。','Format'=>'格式','…get the default page template.'=>'……含默认网页模板。','…get the same page <a href="https://wpapprentice.com/blog/wordpress-theme-vs-template/" target="_blank"><span class="cdp-green">template</span></a> as original.'=>'……含原网页<a href="https://wpapprentice.com/blog/wordpress-theme-vs-template/" target="_blank"><span class="cdp-green">模板</span></a>。','Template'=>'模板','…get no featured image.'=>'……不含特色图片。','…it will set the same <a href="https://firstsiteguide.com/wordpress-featured-image/" target="_blank"><span class="cdp-green">featured image</span></a> as the original.'=>'……含原<a href="https://firstsiteguide.com/wordpress-featured-image/" target="_blank"><span class="cdp-green">特色图片</span></a>。','Featured image'=>'特色图片','…get no content (be completely blank).'=>'……不含内容（即空白）。','…get all the content (text, images, videos and other elements/blocks) from the original.'=>'……含全部内容（文本、图片、视频等元素/区块）。','Content'=>'内容','…get an empty <i>custom</i> excerpt (and default to taking the first 55 words of the post).'=>'……<i>自定义</i>摘要为空（，默认为文章前55个词）。','…get the custom <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/excerpt/" target="_blank"><span class="cdp-green">excerpt</span></a> (post/page summary) of the original (if the original had any).'=>'……含原自定义<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/excerpt/" target="_blank"><span class="cdp-green">摘要</span></a> （文章/网页的小结，如有）。','Excerpt'=>'摘要','…get a blank slug, unless the page is published, then it will generate it automatically.'=>'……别名为空，如果网页已发布，则自动生成。','…get the same <a href="https://kinsta.com/knowledgebase/wordpress-slug/" target="_blank"><span class="cdp-green">slug</span></a> of the original. (However after publishing it 